Check out these activities and showcases happening at the 2005 International CES. Plus, see the full list of <a href="/print/attendees/special_events/default.asp">special events</a> and <a href="/print/attendees/show_floor/special_displays/default.asp">special displays</a> and start filling your calendar now.
